                                                                                               3.14.3e      ENHANCED SECURITY REQUIREMENT
                                                                                                            Ensure that [Assignment: organization-defined systems and system components] are
                                                                                                            included in the scope of the specified enhanced security requirements or are segregated
                                                                                                            in purpose-specific networks.

                                                                                                            ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE
                                                                                                            Determine if:

                                                                                                            3.14.3e_ODP[1]      Systems and system components included in the scope of the specified
                                                                                                                                enhanced security requirements are identified.
                                                                                                            3.14.3e[a]          <3.14.3e_ODP[1]: systems and system components> are included in the
                                                                                                                                scope of the specified enhanced security requirements.
                                                                                                            3.14.3e[b]          Systems and system components that are not included in
                                                                                                                                <3.14.3e_ODP[1]: systems and system components> are segregated in
                                                                                                                                purpose-specific networks.
                                                                                                            POTENTIAL ASSESSMENT METHODS AND OBJECTS
